#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:18
msgid "``server``"
msgstr "``server``"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:19
msgid ""
"End-to-end sanity test against a running LMCache MP cache server (ZMQ + "
"HTTP). Requires the full ``lmcache`` install and a GPU."
