#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:33
msgid "engine"
msgstr "engine"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:35
msgid ""
"The ``lmcache bench engine`` command runs sustained performance "
"benchmarks against an inference engine (e.g., vLLM). It supports multiple"
" workload types that exercise different caching patterns and reports "
"TTFT, decoding speed, and throughput metrics."
msgstr "``lmcache bench engine`` 命令对推理引擎（例如 vLLM）执行持续性能基准测试。它支持多种工作负载类型，用于测试不同的缓存模式，并上报 TTFT、解码速度和吞吐量等指标。"

